name: Strandquist Ann Margaret
description: i am very family oriented woman.I love to treat people the way i desire to be treated because i believe whatever goes around comes around. I decided to join this site to expand my search for love. I am very loving,caring,family oriented,faithful and everything a good man could ever desire to want in every woman. Please only serious minded man who is ready to settle down with a woman as husband and wife should contact me as am not here for any joke or head games. I’d like to find a man who is intelligent and confident and not afraid to try new things. I’d like to find a man who understands that the real secret of a life long relationship (marriage) is a good friendship. That friendship is based on trust, honesty, loyalty and respect, not just for each other, but also self respect. I am also looking for someone who is family-oriented, loves children, someone to be my lover and my best friend whom I can express my feelings to. It would be a dream come true if I could find a person having all of those wonderful characteristics and importantly a man can make a woman feel like a real woman in all aspect of life.
